org.freelte.turbodecoder

Class DecoderFrame

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.freelte.turbodecoder.DecoderFrame

  • public class DecoderFrame
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains the soft output from BCJR, the extrinsic info, and the LLR from demod Decoder out and ext info before the interleaver are postfix with 1. after the interleaver use postfix 2 All of the vectors are read & write accessable
